=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據187條評論，新鮮度94%，平均得分7.8/10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fences_2016/|title=Fences (2016)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2016-12-14|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118151918/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fences_2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分79（滿分100），好評居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fences|title=Fences|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-12-14|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132943/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/fences|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國的[[紐約|紐約]]和[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，電影估計能在首週末從限定戲院中獲得5萬至7萬5000美元的票房。上映後，電影獲得了12萬美元。在進入聖誕節的廣泛上映期間，在其前兩天能獲得1150萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |title=Will ‘Rogue One’ Vanquish The Christmas B.O. Competition? |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-12-15 |archive-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216145243/http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

